data.value: Your client read about the YSL Ourika Community Gardens. Which fragrance would you use to tell him more about this?
Your client is interested in refillable fragrances. Which MYSLF will you present?

The Ourika Community Gardens is an open air-laboratory where plants are grown to be used for YSL Beauty formulas. MYSLF LE PARFUM has a lavender accord whose scent was captured straight from the gardens, offering minty-tea and slightly fruity aromatic notes.
MYSLF EAU DE PARFUM was conceived to be refillable in all formats. Buying the refill helps reduce the use of raw materials and gives you better value per ml.
